<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Mühldorf am Inn</head><p>Der Rat kündigt eine baldige Gesandtschaft wegen Werner Neumeyr an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_99" id="48v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_99_r1l19">Dem Richter vnd Rate der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r1l20">Stat cʒu Müldorff </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_99_r1l21"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her Richter / Vnd <expan>lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> . Als Jr vns <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r1l22">habt von wernher Newmeyrs wegen . das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r1l23">vvir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> . vnd dancken <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> freuntſchaft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r1l24">ſolchs ewrs <expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> als Jr gen vns habt <expan>fleiſſıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r1l25">vnd alſo <expan>vvölle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir etc vt <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_99" id="48v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Dem richter und rate der stat czu Müldorff </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her richter und
                            <expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von Wernher Newmeyrs wegen, das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>. Und dancken
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> freuntschaft solchs ewrs
                                <expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> als ir gen uns habt
                                <expan>fleissikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>. Und also
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir etc. ut
                            <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
